<div class="mb-3"><nav aria-label="breadcrumb"><ol class="breadcrumb small"><li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">首页</a></li><li class="breadcrumb-item active">医学素养</li></ol></nav><h4 class="fw-bold mb-0">🩺 医学素养</h4><small class="text-muted">卫生法学 + 预防医学 · 点击展开查看完整知识</small></div>
<ul class="nav nav-tabs mb-3"><li class="nav-item"><button class="nav-link active" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#tabLaw">⚖️ 卫生法学 (7章)</button></li><li class="nav-item"><button class="nav-link" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#tabPrev">🛡️ 预防医学 (8章)</button></li></ul>
